            <div class="two_card_content">
              <div class="two_card_title font-bold text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl lg:text-3xl pb-2">Achievement: Mongolia - Mapping and Management Strategy</div>
              <div class="two_card-content font-normal text-md sm:text-lg md:text-xl lg:text-2xl"><p>In Mongolia, we worked to understand the extent and state of the huge peatlands of 27,000km2. They used to cover almost 2% of the country, but until recently were in danger of rapidly vanishing due to overgrazing and mining, which resulted in droughts, fires and permafrost thawing. Insufficient information on the distribution, natural functions, threats, and status, contributed to a lack of attention in national development plans and land use planning.</p>
<p><a class="cta-button lightbox" href="https://peatlands.wetlands.org/mongolia-mapping-and-management-strategy/">Read more</a></p>
</div>
            </div>
