          <div class="font-normal text-md sm:text-lg md:text-xl lg:text-2xl">
            <p>Wetlands International Indonesia was an early pioneer in research, starting in 2000 with a project to map peatlands and forests. The resulting research paper ‘Peatlands in Indonesia’ was the foundation for our subsequent research, evidence building and community engagement.</p>
