      <!-- Title Block -->
            <!-- Content Block -->
              <div class="content_container mx-auto w-10/12 md:w-8/12 max-w-4xl">
          <div class="font-normal text-md sm:text-lg md:text-xl lg:text-2xl">
            <p>The Indonesian government quickly established the Peatland Restoration Agency (BRG). The new agency was boosted by the knowledge and experience of a deputy director who trained on peatlands in our fact-finding and community empowerment initiatives. BRG has become a powerful driver of peatland understanding and large-scale restoration, while we continue to advise them on priority setting and focused action. We also succeeded in having the Berbak National Park and Danau Sentarum designated as Ramsar Sites.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
